sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Platform
    participant Server as NeMo Guardrails Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant InputRails as Input Rails Pipeline
    participant Embeddings as Embedding Provider<br/>(local or HTTPS/443)
    participant LLM as Upstream LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OutputRails as Output Rails Pipeline

    Note over Client,OutputRails: Flow 1: Chat Completion with Guardrails

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}
    Server->>InputRails: Execute input rails<br/>(content safety, jailbreak, PII)

    alt Embedding-based rail evaluation
        InputRails->>Embeddings: Generate embeddings<br/>(FastEmbed local or API)
        Embeddings-->>InputRails: Embedding vectors
        InputRails->>InputRails: Annoy ANN similarity check
    end

    alt Input blocked
        InputRails-->>Server: BLOCKED (rail violation)
        Server-->>Client: 200 OK (blocked message)
    else Input passed
        InputRails-->>Server: PASSED
        Server->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer {forwarded token}<br/>TLS 1.2+
        LLM-->>Server: Chat completion response
        Server->>OutputRails: Execute output rails<br/>(hallucination, content safety)

        alt Output blocked/modified
            OutputRails-->>Server: MODIFIED (sanitized response)
        else Output passed
            OutputRails-->>Server: PASSED
        end

        Server-->>Client: JSON response (completion or blocked)
    end

    Note over Client,OutputRails: Flow 2: Guardrail Check (No LLM Generation)

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}
    Server->>InputRails: Validate messages against rails<br/>(role-based routing)

    alt Content safety model needed
        InputRails->>LLM: POST content safety check<br/>Bearer Token / API key<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
        LLM-->>InputRails: Safety evaluation result
    end

    InputRails-->>Server: RailsResult<br/>(PASSED / MODIFIED / BLOCKED)
    Server-->>Client: 200 OK {status, output}

    Note over Client,OutputRails: Flow 3: Embedding-based Guardrail Evaluation

    Server->>Embeddings: Generate embeddings<br/>(FastEmbed local or OpenAI/NIM API)
    Embeddings-->>Server: Embedding vectors
    Server->>Server: Annoy Index lookup<br/>(approximate nearest neighbor)
    Server->>LLM: Similarity-based rail evaluation<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+ Bearer Token
    LLM-->>Server: Evaluation result
